com.turn.ttorrent.common.protocol

Interface TrackerMessage.AnnounceRequestMessage

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTTPAnnounceRequestMessage, UDPAnnounceRequestMessage
    Enclosing class:
    TrackerMessage

    public static interface TrackerMessage.AnnounceRequestMessage
    Base interface for announce request messages.

    This interface must be implemented by all subtypes of announce request messages for the various tracker protocols.

    Author:
    mpetazzoni
